    <item>
      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0253回】　與自己的戰鬥</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0201-0300/t-0253-self-vs-self/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2026 19:29:00 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0201-0300/t-0253-self-vs-self/</guid>
      <description>&lt;style&gt;
  /* 1. 標題縮小 */
